<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Tarots_cards_deal.jpg" class="image" title="Modern French-style 78-card Tarot."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/df/Tarots_cards_deal.jpg/180px-Tarots_cards_deal.jpg" width="180" height="133" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Tarots_cards_deal.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
